{
  "stem": "26111.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "My earliest-- I can't tell exactly, but I'm sure that it was something like-- it was during my first year at the elementary school, which starts at five at that time.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Or five is a kind of a kindergarten class.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "So kindergarten was five.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "It was during that year that I heard-- on my way home from school, I was walking-- wasn't that far-- I heard some boys talking loudly behind me.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And I heard some words repeated again and again.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And then the equivalent of, hey, you, since I didn't pay any attention.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And [LAUGHS] I really, literally, probably didn't know what, what they were-- what they were doing, what they were aiming at.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And so, so I said, yes, very attentively, you know, yes, do you want something?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so they started spewing these, these words at me, et cetera.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I was absolutely horrified.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was-- no, I, I had really no idea.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I thought they'd got the wrong-- the wrong child.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They're making a mistake.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I just sort of beat a hasty retreat because I thought they were slightly deranged, actually.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So that was my first experience of-- practical experience of anti-Semitism.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I wish all others had been as, as peaceful as that one.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So-- [SIGHS] Do you recall the words, the actual German words, that were spoken by those children?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, [SIGHS] it would be-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I, I don't really.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It would be all kinds of what they imagined to be Yiddish versions of German curses.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It would be all kinds of Jewish names. 'Itzik' would be one, which was presumably their way that they thought 'Yitzhak' was-- was pronounced.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And so this was supposed to be an insult, simply-- merely by dint of being a Jewish name.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
